member.summary:
Composite attack item that aggregates a collection of instances. and return the sums of all children; returns the maximum child range.
Implements so collection-initialiser syntax works:
var combo = new CompositeAttackItem("Battle Kit") { sword, axe, magicStaff };

member.remarks:
World size is loaded from :

var config = GameConfig.Load("game.xml");
var world  = new World(config.MaxX, config.MaxY);
